{"title":"wsl2配置问题？未解决","slug":"wsl2配置问题？未解决","date":"2025-07-06T03:32:02.000Z","updated":"2025-07-06T03:34:39.101Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/wsl2配置问题？未解决.json","photos":[],"excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<p>奇了怪了，我按照官方文档写的wsl2配置一直失效，重启重装wsl子系统都没有解决这个问题，如下是我的配置，因为我想在wsl2中直接使用Windows的代理</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight toml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">[wsl2]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">networkingMode</span>=mirrored</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">dnsTunneling</span>=<span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">firewall</span>=<span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">autoProxy</span>=<span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>不过直接原因还是wsl2配置有点麻烦，核心问题： wsl2是docker运行的虚拟机，这就导致：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>wsl2和Windows本机的127.0.0.1不是同一个，如果wsl2要想访问Windows的服务，或者Windows想要访问wsl2的服务，这时候这俩本质上是在一个局域网里的，要用局域网的ip地址</li>\n</ul>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}